guretzki as part of pivot-contrib

Packages
pivot_contrib.guretzki This package has two functions: It's the root of all source of the guretzki part of the Apache Extras pivot-contrib project and it contains all classes that can sensibly be used from within .bxml files.
pivot_contrib.guretzki.awtlink Classes in this package allow using Pivot Components within AWT Dialogs.
pivot_contrib.guretzki.bxmlbrowser Functionality for developers: Two ways of invoking a helper application that allows easy reloading of .bxml files to immeditately preview the effects of changes.
pivot_contrib.guretzki.test Hosts test and/ or example classes for the guretzki part of the Apache Extras pivot-contrib project
